name: L-threonylcarbamoyladenylate synthase
reaction: L-threonine + ATP + HCO3- = L-threonylcarbamoyladenylate + diphosphate + H2O [RN:R10463]
comment: The enzyme is involved in the synthesis of N6-threonylcarbamoyladenosine37 in tRNAs, with the anticodon NNU, i.e. tRNAIle, tRNAThr, tRNAAsn, tRNALys, tRNASer and tRNAArg [6].
